prediction.sparql:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?notableTypeLabel ?description WHERE {
  fb:m.09482 fb:common.topic.notable_types ?notableType .
  ?notableType rdfs:label ?notableTypeLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?notableTypeLabel ) = 'en' ) .
  fb:m.09482 fb:common.topic.description ?description .
  FILTER ( lang( ?description ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?draft_year WHERE {
  ?draft_pick fb:sports.draft_pick.draftee fb:m.097yk7 .
  ?draft_pick fb:sports.draft_pick.draft ?draft_event .
  ?draft_event fb:time.event.start_date ?draft_year .
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  fb:m.01s3vk fb:film.film.starring ?performance .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.character fb:m.0gmm518 .
  ?actor fb:type.object.name ?actorName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?actorName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?team ?teamLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0dr5g9 fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?team .
  ?team rdfs:label ?teamLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?teamLabel ) = 'en' ) ?team fb:type.object.type fb:sports.sports_team .

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?person ?personLabel ?from ?to WHERE {
  fb:m.060m4 fb:government.government_office_or_title.office_holders ?positionHeld .
  ?positionHeld fb:government.government_position_held.office_holder ?person .
  ?positionHeld fb:government.government_position_held.from ?from .
  ?positionHeld fb:government.government_position_held.to ?to .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?personLabel ) = "en" )
  }
  FILTER ( ?from <= "1993-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ?to >= "1993-01-01" ^^ xsd:date )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?spouseName WHERE {
  fb:m.0cm83 fb:people.person.spouse_s ?spouse .
  ?spouse fb:people.marriage.spouse fb:m.0cm63 .
  fb:m.0cm63 fb:type.object.name ?spouseName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?spouseName ) = "" || LANGMATCHES( LANG( ?spouseName ) , "en" ) )
}
LIMIT 1

  ?symbolRel fb:location.location_symbol_relationship.symbol ?animal .
  ?symbolRel fb:location.location_symbol_relationship.Kind_of_symbol fb:m.0462793 .

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?spouseName WHERE {

  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?spouse .
  FILTER ( ?spouse != fb:m.0hz_1 ) .
  ?spouse fb:type.object.name ?spouseName .

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?college ?collegeLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0c2yrf fb:people.person.education ?education .
  ?education fb:education.education.institution ?college .
  ?college rdfs:label ?collegeLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?collegeLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?collegeLabel ) , "university" ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?professionLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0btx2g rdfs:label ?label FILTER ( lang( ?label ) = 'en' ) .
  fb:m.0btx2g fb:people.person.profession ?profession .
  ?profession rdfs:label ?professionLabel
  FILTER ( lang( ?professionLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?stateLabel ?countryLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.05kkh rdfs:label ?stateLabel .
  fb:m.05kkh fb:location.location.containedby ?country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?stateLabel ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( lang( ?countryLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ( SUBSTR( ?label , 1 , 4 ) AS ?year ) WHERE {
  fb:m.01d6g fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?label ) , "world series" ) ) FILTER ( REGEX( SUBSTR( ?label , 1 , 4 ) , "^\\d{4}$" ) )
}
ORDER BY ?year

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?award ?awardLabel ?year ?workLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0fb1q fb:award.award_winner.awards_won ?award .
  ?award a fb:award.award_honor .
  ?award fb:award.award_honor.award_winner fb:m.0fb1q .
  ?award fb:award.award_honor.award ?awardCategory .
  ?awardCategory rdfs:label ?awardLabel .
  ?award fb:award.award_honor.year ?year .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?award fb:award.award_honor.honored_for ?work .
    ?work rdfs:label ?workLabel .
  }
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?awardLabel ) , "grammy" ) ) FILTER ( LANG( ?awardLabel ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY ?year

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  fb:m.019nnl fb:tv.tv_program.regular_cast ?performance .
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_performance.character fb:m.035szd .
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_performance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor rdfs:label ?actorName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?actorName ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?startDate WHERE {
  fb:m.0jmfb fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?startDate .
}
ORDER BY ?startDate
LIMIT 1

  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?teamName ) , "mercury" ) || CONTAINS( LCASE( ?teamName ) , "wnba" ) )

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?spouseName WHERE {
  fb:m.05np4c fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?spouse .
  FILTER ( ?spouse != fb:m.05np4c ) ?spouse rdfs:label ?spouseName

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?championship ?endDate WHERE {
  fb:m.0713r fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:sports.sports_championship_event.champion fb:m.0713r .
  ?championship fb:time.event.end_date ?endDate .
  ?championship fb:type.object.name ?name .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?name ) , "world series" ) )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?endDate )
